***********  HTTP STATUS CODES *****************

The Status-Code element in a server response, is a 3-digit integer where the first digit of the Status-Code defines the class of response and the last two digits do not 

have any categorization role. There are 5 values for the first digit .

https://www.tutorialspoint.com/http/http_status_codes.htm
